<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-04-01T00:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-04-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="10" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d10">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">710 Consultation 4/4–146: Circular
                            telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to <gloss type="to">Diplomatic Representatives in
                                    the American Republics Except Argentina and
                                Haiti</gloss></hi><note n="26" xml:id="d10fn26">This circular was
                                sent to Buenos Aires and to Port-au-Prince “as secret information
                                only”.</note></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi></seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-04-01T00:00:00-05:00">April 1,
                                1946—midnight.</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Please see <gloss target="#t_FonMin1">FonMin</gloss> at once and submit
                            memo embodying text quoted in immediately following circular
                                telegram<note n="27" xml:id="d10fn27"><hi rend="italic">Infra</hi>.</note> and stating that if majority of Govts agree with
                            our position we propose to make a public statement thereof on or about
                            Apr 8. Memo should add that we hope Govt to which you are accredited
                            will authorize us to express its concurrence with our position or will
                            make a public statement along similar lines on same date.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>